      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 7th level</em><br />As an action, you gain the ability to see through solid objects to a range of 30 feet. Within that range, you have darkvision if you do not already have it. This special sight lasts for 1 minute or until your concentration ends (as if you were concentrating on a spell). During that time, you perceive objects as ghostly, transparent images.</p><p>Once you use this invocation, you cannot use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
